      • subscribe

        public void subscribe​(Subscriptor.Lambda updateFunction,
                      Entity en)
        Create a subscription on Orion. This operation put the Id, Function on a Hashmap. If the id already is in the hashMap, the function is added to list.
        Parameters:
        updateFunction - a function which does a update when came a notification.
        en - a entity object representing the entity

      • subscribe

        public void subscribe​(Subscriptor.Lambda updateFunction,
                      java.util.List<Device> deviceList)
        Create a subscription on Orion. This operation put the Id, Function on a Hashmap. If the id already is in the hashMap, the function is added to list. Note: this method overload subscribe, receiving instead of one single entity to a list of entities
        Parameters:
        updateFunction - a function which does a update when came a notification.
        deviceList - a entity list of object representing the lists
        See Also:
        subscribe(Lambda, Entity)

      • subscribe

        public void subscribe​(Subscriptor.Lambda updateFunction,
                      java.util.List<java.lang.String> conditionsList,
                      java.util.List<Device> deviceList)
        Create a subscription on Orion. this subscription reacts (trigger notifications) to a attribute list This operation put the Id, Function on a Hashmap. If the id already is in the hashMap, the function is added to list. Note: this method overload subscribe, receiving instead of one single entity to a list of entities
        Parameters:
        updateFunction - a function which does a update when came a notification.
        deviceList - a entity list of object representing the lists
        conditionsList - a list containing all trigger conditions to send a notification.
        See Also:
        subscribe(Lambda, Entity)

      • subscribeAndListen

        public void subscribeAndListen​(Subscriptor.Lambda updateFunction,
                               Entity model)
        Create a subscription on Orion and listen to notifications. When a notification come, a update function associated with entity is applied to entity values. Notice that this method is unblocking using threads.
        Parameters:
        updateFunction - a function which does a update when came a notification.
        model - a object representing the Entity.

      • subscribeAndListen

        public void subscribeAndListen​(Subscriptor.Lambda updateFunction,
                               Entity model,
                               Device device)
        Create a subscription on Orion and listen to notifications. When a notification come, a update function associated with entity is applied to entity values. Notice that method is unblocking using threads.
        Parameters:
        updateFunction - a function which does a update when came a notification.
        model - a object representing the Entity.
        device - a device object which represents the entity.

      • subscribeAndListenBlocking

        public <T> java.util.List<T> subscribeAndListenBlocking​(Subscriptor.Lambda updateFunction,
                                                        Entity model)
        Create a subscription on Orion and listen to notifications. When a notification come, a update function associated with entity is applied to entity values. Notice that method is blocking call, so the subscriber will be waiting until came a notification.
        Parameters:
        updateFunction - a function which does a update when came a notification.
        model - a object representing the Entity which want to retrieve.
        Returns:
        a list of updated entities.

      • showStackTrace

        public void showStackTrace​(java.lang.Exception e)

        Parameters:
        e - a exception to show your stack trace on console.
